They had a big meeting in the heavens,

9
00:00:55,430 --> 00:01:01,390
all the thirty-five crores (3.5 million)

10
00:01:02,510 --> 00:01:09,070
of Gods, the deities were there present

11
00:01:13,190 --> 00:01:17,110
to decide what is to be done.

12
