and that permission You must give us,

174
00:15:03,301 --> 00:15:05,101
otherwise we are not for this work".

175
00:15:05,661 --> 00:15:08,701
They formed a union against Me.

176
00:15:12,741 --> 00:15:14,941
And I had to give in.

177
00:15:15,221 --> 00:15:19,021
