179
00:15:22,061 --> 00:15:25,341
You're not to do that, don't have to do that.

180
00:15:27,381 --> 00:15:29,861
Don't play with my money,

181
00:15:30,741 --> 00:15:36,461
don't take my hospitality, be careful.

182
00:15:36,901 --> 00:15:40,421
I tell you as much as I can,

183
00:15:41,941 --> 00:15:43,541
and this is what it is.

184
00:15:43,941 --> 00:15:47,861
One side is Mahamaya, another side these deities,

185
00:15:48,101 --> 00:15:50,701
and poor Sahaja Yogis in between.

186
00:15:55,741 --> 00:15:58,901
I sympathise with you, I know

187
00:15:59,581 --> 00:16:02,301
but you better be careful.

188
00:16:02,621 --> 00:16:05,341
It's a razor's edge I think, of course,

189
00:16:05,821 --> 00:16:07,981
but otherwise it's wonderful.

190
00:16:09,741 --> 00:16:15,581
If these two things, if you know, that this is Mahamaya

191
00:16:16,461 --> 00:16:20,141
and that the deities are around sitting now here, all of them,

192
00:16:20,421 --> 00:16:24,981
peering into you, all of them,

193
00:16:25,221 --> 00:16:28,181
judging you, having a big meeting there. Who's who?

194
00:16:28,661 --> 00:16:31,621
