200
00:16:57,461 --> 00:17:02,861
And it's already predicted that the whole world will

201
00:17:03,101 --> 00:17:06,021
come down at the Lotus Feet of your Mother,

202
00:17:06,301 --> 00:17:11,741
and that you will decide the future of this world.

203
00:17:12,021 --> 00:17:14,741
It is written already, fourteen-thousand years back,

204
00:17:15,061 --> 00:17:17,941
and there's another one who's prophesizing the same.

205
00:17:29,541 --> 00:17:31,941
So you have to be aware.

206
00:17:32,941 --> 00:17:35,381
Where is your attention?

207
00:17:42,101 --> 00:17:44,541
What are you worried about?

208
00:17:44,941 --> 00:17:47,901
Where are you spending your time?

209
00:17:49,101 --> 00:17:51,821
Leave your children to me.

210
00:17:53,221 --> 00:17:55,661
Leave your families to me.

211
00:17:56,221 --> 00:17:58,981
You can only keep your purse,

212
00:18:01,101 --> 00:18:04,021
but the rest of it,

213
00:18:05,941 --> 00:18:08,661
you can leave all your headaches to Me.

214
00:18:10,301 --> 00:18:13,821
But don't play tricks with Me.

215
00:18:15,861 --> 00:18:22,021
Mahamaya knows all your tricks, everything, in and out.

216
00:18:23,301 --> 00:18:26,821
If I want to know, I can know each and everything about you.

217
00:18:27,381 --> 00:18:30,061
I don't want to know.

218
00:18:33,941 --> 00:18:37,301
Under these circumstances

219
00:18:39,261 --> 00:18:43,381
we are supported, looked after,

220
00:18:45,261 --> 00:18:50,101
managed, taken to reality so easily,

221
00:18:50,941 --> 00:18:54,661
so much, with care.

222
00:18:55,127 --> 00:18:57,260
You tell me "Mother, suddenly I went there

223
00:18:57,461 --> 00:19:00,101
and what do I find, Sahaja Yogis sitting there.

224
00:19:00,621 --> 00:19:03,341
And we wanted to know someone. He was just there.

225
00:19:03,701 --> 00:19:05,661
How is it?"

226
00:19:09,541 --> 00:19:12,821
You are assisted.

227
00:19:13,101 --> 00:19:16,741
Here these Prime Ministers have only five, six bodyguards,

228
00:19:17,021 --> 00:19:22,141
you have millions and millions, each one of you, with you.

229
00:19:23,861 --> 00:19:28,021
Nobody can touch you except for you can harm yourself that's all.

230
00:19:28,501 --> 00:19:30,461
Nobody can harm you.

231
00:19:31,221 --> 00:19:35,541
So today, again a day of great determination,

232
00:19:37,141 --> 00:19:39,101
and taking a vow

233
00:19:39,381 --> 00:19:44,661
that for us, our ascent is the only concern,

234
00:19:45,467 --> 00:19:49,587
is the only idea, nothing else,

235
00:19:50,547 --> 00:19:52,347
and it will work out.

236
00:19:52,907 --> 00:19:56,427
All the rest will be taken care of.

237
00:19:57,187 --> 00:19:59,587
You have all the mechanics to do that,

238
00:20:00,027 --> 00:20:04,707
but first give it to the mechanics to work out.

239
00:20:05,107 --> 00:20:07,747
All will work in a reflex action.

240
00:20:08,147 --> 00:20:11,267
Clear, clear out your chakras.

241
00:20:11,827 --> 00:20:14,307
Don't say "I have this, I have that." Just clear out.

242
00:20:14,627 --> 00:20:17,227
"How dare I have all these problems."

243
00:20:17,827 --> 00:20:20,907
How dare I have all these chakras still lingering.

244
00:20:21,427 --> 00:20:25,947
Clear out, morning, evening. Clear out.

245
00:20:30,547 --> 00:20:32,267
I'm sure it will work out.

246
00:20:32,547 --> 00:20:37,067
Next year I hope I'll have some good news.

247
00:20:37,987 --> 00:20:39,679
May God Bless You.

